---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AmicBridge – Connect with Trusted Lenders and Borrowers">
  <section class="text-center py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-950 via-blue-900 to-indigo-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight">
        Building <span class="text-blue-400">Trust</span> Between People, Not Institutions
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-12">
        AmicBridge is a private community where verified members connect directly —
        lenders, borrowers, and investors working together safely and transparently.
        We don’t handle money — we build verified bridges between people who do.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-slate-800/70 backdrop-blur-sm inline-block px-10 py-8 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-slate-700">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-300 mb-2">Private Membership Access</h2>
        <p class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">$100 <span class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-400">(one-time access fee)</span></p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 max-w-md mx-auto">
          Membership gives you verified access to our private contact network — where trusted
          lenders and borrowers meet directly, with safety and confidentiality ensured.
        </p>

        <a
          href="https://wa.me/4791234567?text=Hi%20AmicBridge%2C%20I%27d%20like%20to%20join%20the%20network%20and%20verify%20my%20payment."
          target="_blank"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition transform hover:scale-105 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg"
        >
          💬 Contact Us on WhatsApp to Join
        </a>

        <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-sm italic">
          After manual payment verification, you’ll receive your secure private access link.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-24 px-6 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-8">Why People Trust AmicBridge</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-700">
      <li>🤝 Verified, one-to-one introductions to genuine lenders and borrowers</li>
      <li>🔒 Private and encrypted communication channels</li>
      <li>🌍 A growing network of real, verified members worldwide</li>
      <li>🧩 Simple, transparent access — one fee, lifetime membership</li>
      <li>👥 Dedicated human support every step of the way</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-blue-950 text-white py-20 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Our Promise</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Every AmicBridge member is verified before access is granted.  
        Payments are confirmed manually to ensure safety and transparency.  
        You’re not sending money into a system — you’re joining a verified network built on trust.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
